headline: Kimberly-Clark Appoints John Carmichael as President, North America
summary: Kimberly-Clark Corporation (NASDAQ: KMB) today announced the appointment of John Carmichael as President, North America, effective September 15th. Carmichael succeeds interim President Kurt Laufer, who will resume his prior role as President of U.S. Consumer Sales.
